title: The Great Bongo Heist
description: The boys forget to get Chata a gift for Abuela Day and in a panicked move, they pretend that the bongo drums they borrowed from Xochi are for her. Knowing they have to return the drums, Victor & Valentino pretend to be burglars to steal the bongos back.

title: Transylbabies
description: A mission to babysit Snowmanpire babies in Transylbiria leads Vambre and Prohyas to attack the local monster townsfolk in misguided attempts to keep the Snowbabies safe.

title: Diversion en Tokio, Parte 1: Ataque de los Bichos
description: En una visita a Tokio, el equipo de Tennyson se enfrenta a un secreto horrible: los Bugg Brothers están manejando el nuevo restaurante de moda en Japón como parte de un plan perverso para ganar un montón de dinero a costa de un público desprevenido.

title: #WorkingStiff
description: After Babs hooks Karen up with a job at the Burrito Bucket the two heroes encounter a new villain, the scourge of the fast-food underworld, the Condiment King!

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Little Mer-Tiger
description: The origin of Tiger is told as a flashback.  As the legend goes, Tiger used to be a mermaid.  One day the evil ruler of the sea, Bubble Grandpa, demanded a hamburger and picked Tiger to retrieve it.  He used his magic sea powers to give Tiger legs and send her ashore.  But Tiger grew to love the land, and with the help of her new friend, Uncle Grandpa, defeated the evil sea ruler and got to keep her legs.

title: Za
description: Pizza's Diner needs a makeover. Apple and Onion better get this right or Pizza is ruined.

title: Schnorp
description: The Thunderkittens plug a new video game cartridge into Snarf only to learn that it didn't load a game, it loaded a whole new personality into their pal! Meet Schnorp, a kind Swedish man who loves the beauty of nature and collecting berries! Schnorp is loads of fun, but we're gonna want Snarf back, right?

title: Be Afraid of the Dark
description: Ben travels into space to thwart Ghostfreak's diabolical plans. But is he hero enough to take on the Mummy, Werewolf and Frankenstein?

title: Council of the Creek: Operation Hive-Mind
description: Hive Mind - When bees take over the Trading Tree, Craig must assemble the Council of the Creek to avert disaster.

title: Drawn to Sports with Zachary
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Zachary loves competing and developing his skills in karate.

title: Swept Away
description: Pocoyo shows us that tidying can be fun too: a broom can be a horse, a guitar, or even a hockey stick!

title: My Clique
description: Chloe, a child prodigy, finds it difficult to connect with her much older classmates. The Bears take her under their wing and show her how to make great college friends.

title: The Color of Monkey
description: Everybody's favorite alien conman, Argit, takes on a shady sidekick, Simian, in a shocking new business.

title: Little Dude
description: While Finn and Jake go swimming, Finn's hat magically comes to life!

title: Bubble Buddies
description: Steven looks like a hero when he forms a magic crystal bubble around himself to protect a girl he likes from danger, but then panics when he can't figure out how to turn the bubble off!

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: La Formula de Manzana
description: Manzana necesita encontrar una fórmula divertida que le permita conseguir un papel cómico en una película.

title: Professor Proofed
description: After the Professor's latest experiment goes awry, the girls become overprotective.

title: Fire Maker
description: The Ice Emperor learns of the ninja's arrival and sends his Blizzard Samurai warriors to destroy them and the villagers who sheltered them.

title: Lucky Ducky Mug
description: When Adorabat and Badgerclops break Mao Mao's favorite mug, he gives them the silent treatment.

title: Swing
description: Meet Bing and his friends… Join us and celebrate the noisy, joyful, messy reality of preschool life.

title: Don't Read the Comments
description: An obsession with comments and criticisms about him on the Board of Opinions drives Prohyas nuts, affecting Warrior missions for the worse and raising Vambre's ire, I mean, concerns.

title: Superstar Dan/Awesome Brawlers on Vacation
description: Superstar Dan: The Awesome Brawler's head to Tokyo for the Bakugan Battle League - Tokyo Edition. While Wynton, Shun, Lia and Lightning see the sites, and enjoy the tastes of Japan, Dan, as the Los Volmos Champion, has official Bakugan Battle League duties and obligations that keep him busy./Awesome Brawlers on Vacation: Lia, Lightning, Shun and Wynton explore the sights of Toyko when a rogue Bakugan shows up and rampages. The Awesome Brawlers have to spring into action, rolling out their Bakugan to stop the rogue enemy before any real damage can be done.

title: Charlie Ball
description: After Panda gets injured on the basketball court, the Bears invite Charlie to be on their basketball team. But when Charlie gets too good, he starts to ruin all the fun of the game.

title: Let's Meet Sonic
description: When world class hero SONIC THE HEDGEHOG visits the plaza, he teams up with KO to save the day.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Just Wait in the Car
description: As Mary runs errands, Clarence waits in the car and struggles to fight boredom.

title: A Domar Los Cielos Peligrosos
description: Con el ala del avión no tripulado de Axel roto, el equipo debe encontrar otra forma de detener a Madcap y sus secuaces mientras se lanzan a los cielos en aviones de juguete para un asalto aéreo en el parque de la ciudad.

title: El Hacedor de Fuego
description: El Emperador de Hielo se entera de la llegada de los ninjas y envía a sus guerreros Samurais Blizzard a destruirlos, y a todos los aldeanos que los albergaron.

title: Like a Duck to Water
description: Daffy overcomes his fear of the swimming pool.

title: Vreedlemania
description: Pa Vreedle reunites with Ma for all-out destruction.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Wednesday - Part 4
description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

title: From Hedorium to Eternity
description: 11-year-old Ben, Gwen, and friends go on the adventure of a lifetime in their own backyard.

title: Oh My Compost
description: When Sushi-Mushi breaks the only spoon he has ever cooked with, he declares his cooking days are over! So Mush-Mush and friends step up to cook for everyone instead. How hard can it be? It turns out, very! The Mushlers will have to convince Sushi-Mushi he's still the best compost chef, even without his favorite spoon!

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Battle for the Bottled City
description: Atom shrinks Superman so he can visit his fellow Kryptonians in the bottled city of Kandor. Soon after, Brainiac attacks and takes off with the bottle. Atom is forced to take control of one of Superman's damaged robots in order to follow after Brainiac and retrieve the city.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Craig and the Kid's Table
description: It's a Williams Family Thanksgiving, which means it's time to reunite The Kid's Table! But when Bernard accidentally destroys dessert, Craig uses the power of the Kids Table to help save his brother from certain grounding.

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: Rock Show
description: Chad's band Dogmon, plays a show for the first time in years, giving Clarence and Mary a chance to really rock out.

title: Snow Month
description: After a snow day saves Blossom from having to face a boy who's asked her out, she decides to use her ice breath to keep it going even if that means plunging Townsville into eternal winter complete with monstrous yetis!

title: Los Puntos
description: iGumball y Darwin aceptan hacer todas las tareas de Tobias a cambio de "puntos buenos"!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Thingameroo
description: When a lack of motivation threatens to sink the kids' chances in the Sportslete Athlaction Awards, they create the greatest mascot of all time to boost school spirit.

title: Thanksgetting
description: It's Thanksgiving but the Titans are sick of the normal traditions so they create their own.

title: Voleibol
description: Steven está decidido a ayudar a la Perla original de Diamante Rosa para sanar la cicatriz en su rostro.

title: Back to the Library
description: Uncle Grandpa uses time travel to convince his past self to return a library book on time.

title: Miguelito the Mosquito
description: When Miguelito begins to outshine Victor as the town daredevil, Vic attempts to sabotage him in order to bring the attention back to himself.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Apoca-lice Now
description: When Chef brokers a truce with lice by selecting three kids to "host" them on their heads, Courtney instigates a kid vs. lice war.

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Tim Buk-TV
description: Team Tennyson heads to the Okefenokee Swamp to witness the blooming of the Blushing Orchid, something that happens once every one hundred years. But their plans get disrupted when Tim Buk-Tu, trying to make his new 'reality' show more exciting, endangers the rare flower and everyone else at the swamp.

title: La Venganza es Mia
description: Aspheera llega al Monasterio de Spinjitzu y se enfrenta a Wu, obligando a uno de los ninjas a hacer un sacrificio heroico.

title: Weiner Takes All
description: After forgetting to book a Hot Diggity Doggity Dog mascot on National Hotdog Day, Chef tries to pass off an Australian man dressed as a kangaroo as a substitute.

title: Gobble Head
description: Chef accidentally cooks up a killer cyborg turkey in a failed attempt to get the kids to appreciate him on Appreciation Day.

title: The Other Fight
description: Eliminated from the Bakugan Battle League, Ajit is airlifted by drone to a massive cargo ship in the middle of Tokyo Bay. Now that he's on board the cargo ship, he must rescue Dan and Drago, and stop whoever is sabotaging the Battle League. Dan and Ajit investigate the mysterious cargo ship that the eliminated brawlers and Bakugan are being held on. Dan races to track down Drago, but along the way runs into a familiar face.

title: Memory Amok
description: When Puppycorn witnesses Unikitty do the most embarrassing thing ever, he vows he will never forget it. Desperate, Unikitty uses Dr. Fox's memory machine to erase Puppycorn's memory of the embarrassing event. In the process, Unikitty accidentally releases all of Puppycorn's memories. Now she and the gang must scramble to capture all the scampering memories, or Puppycorn will forget his life.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: The Case of Porky's Pants/Fully Vetted
description: Detective Daffy takes on the case of Porky's missing pants. Tweety's trip to the veterinarian's office gives Sylvester the perfect opportunity for a lunchtime treat.

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: Best Day Ever
description: Joker frees Luthor with a mother box and forces him to spend the day together, hopping all over the world, with the Justice League hot on their trail trying to catch up.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: King of the Machines
description: Panthro gets insecure when he finds out Barbastella has a history of dating royalty, so he tries to impress her by becoming "King of the Machines" and giving all the appliances in the Cats' Lair artificial intelligence.

title: Escape de Bahia Bebe
description: Cuando, por accidente, Vic y Val se convierten a sí mismos y a Don en bebés, deben escapar de una guardería para poder volver a sus edades normales.

title: Beat Your Greens/Down N' Dirty
description: Beat Your Greens: When Broccoli Aliens from space invade Townsville, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls and all the children of Townsville to take a bite out of crime. Down N' Dirty: When Buttercup refuses to take a bath, the town kicks her out. But Buttercup decides to stick with her stink until her favorite thing is taken away from her.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Appleoni
description: The wrong person is getting credit for a new dance craze.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Walnuts & Rain
description: Finn & Jake stumble into two different holes and meet two different fates.

title: Vengeance Is Mine!
description: Aspheera arrives at the Monastery of Spinjitzu and confronts Wu, forcing one of the ninja to make a heroic sacrifice.

title: Ranger Tabes
description: To recover a missing package, the Bears get help from Ranger Tabes, an eccentric forest ranger. But her overblown sense of justice might be too much for the Bears to handle.

title: Twisted Sister/Cover Up
description: Twisted Sister: The girls decide they need some help fighting crime so they create another Powerpuff Girl. But they don't get the combination of sugar, spice and everything nice quite right./Cover Up: Blossom and Bubbles learn that Buttercup has secretly been rubbing a security blanket before every battle to make herself a super fighter. Can the girls convince Buttercup that her strength is within?

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Tea Timer's Ball
description: The Tea Timers throw a dance and invite everyone in the Creek. Craig believes it's solely to prank him, while Kelsey deals with an unwanted admirer.

title: Banda de por Vida
description: Cuando Vic y Val acompañan a Xochi a un concierto punk, quieren demostrar que son lo suficientemente geniales para salir con ella. Pero en un intento desesperado por tener onda, terminan arruinando el concierto.

title: Shun and Lightning/Premonition of a Storm
description: Shun and Lightning: Shun and Lightning are on the hunt for a rare Tumpee, when they run into McQ! With all the devices related crimes happening in Los Volmos, Shun decides to investigate to try to get to the bottom of McQ's nefarious dealings./Premonition of a Storm: After a run in with McQ, Shun and Lightning find themselves in a little bit trouble. They're trapped!  Tied up with no Bakugan to help them escape, and no one knows their whereabouts. It will take some big help to help them get out of this mess.

title: Madtrap
description: Madcap and Princess SugarSalt trap Axel and the team inside a Minergy-powered labyrinth that attacks them with their greatest fears, forcing them to work together and escape as a unit.

title: Wednesday - Part 3
description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

title: Slumber Party
description: A thunderstorm forces Chloe to spend the night at the Cave with the Bears. When Chloe's parents tell the Bears to protect Chloe, they take the task a bit too seriously.

title: The Ape
description: Ms Simian sets out to "befriend" Gumball in order to win a Favourite Teacher Award.

title: You're a Good Friend, KO
description: KO brings Dendy along for a hero mission in order to cheer her up.

title: Recuerdos Locos
description: Cuando Perricornio ve a Unikitty hacer la cosa más vergonzosa de la historia, jura que nunca lo olvidará. Desesperada, Unikitty utiliza la máquina de memoria de la Dra. Fox para borrar el recuerdo de Perricornio del embarazoso evento. En el proceso, Unikitty libera accidentalmente todos los recuerdos de Perricornio. Ahora ella y su pandilla deben capturar todos los recuerdos de prisa, o Perricornio olvidará su vida.

title: Boo-ray for Bizarro
description: When the diabolical Amazo attacks the League and begins to steal their powers one-by-one, the klutzy, backwards-thinking Bizarro becomes our heroes' last hope to turn things around.

title: The Return of Aunt Grandma
description: Aunt Grandma is back and still bent on ruining Uncle Grandpa.

title: The Cave of Gelatinous Doom!
description: The Warriors don't have a worthy adventure to use their impressive new skull-and-crossbones-emblazoned Bonehead Magisword until they are sent on a quest to battle a mighty slime beast in the Dungeon of Gelatinous Doom!

title: Officer Moody
description: Pieces of Mr. Reese's past are revealed when his old partner on the police force, Officer Moody, visits Aberdale Elementary.

title: Carl
description: A pleasant weekend goes awry when a monster attacks.

title: The Granny Trap
description: The kids discover that Nevin's Granny Grancie has an estranged sister/best friend, Granny Grindle. Nevin and Lil' Lemon, with Seth's help, vow to reunite them! But getting these old friends back together may test their own friendship.

title: The Thing in the Wall
description: When Axel and the team accuse Galileo of stealing their possessions, the lizard must hunt down the true culprit - a mysterious creature behind the wall - to prove his innocence.

title: Pencil Break Mania
description: When Pencil Break Mania hits the Creek, JP finds himself as an unlikely champion and is forced to defend his title against the very best!

title: The Thanksgiving Special
description: The park guys need to get Thanksgiving dinner for their families to save Thanksgiving.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: El Gran Robo de Bongos
description: Los chicos olvidan conseguir un regalo para Chata en el Día de la Abuela y en un movimiento desesperado, le regalan los bongos que pidieron prestados a Xochi. Sabiendo que deben devolver los tambores, Victor y Valentino fingen ser ladrones para robar los instrumentos.

title: Letras Desastrosas
description: La pandilla está planeando una sorpresa para Puppycorn, así que deletrean las cosas cuando hablan para que él no se entere. Desesperado por saber lo que dicen, Puppycorn encuentra un libro mágico que cree que lo ayudará a aprender a deletrear, ipero sin saberlo, el libro le enseña a lanzar hechizos! ¿Se dará cuenta Puppycorn de que el conocimiento es poder, y de que algunos secretos se guardan por una razón?

title: The Vegging
description: Gumball and Darwin want to have a lazy day on the sofa, and have come up with various tricks to stop themselves having to move. Gradually more and more people arrive, seemingly to get them to move, until finally they realize that if they have to move, they'll do it in the laziest way possible.

title: Diversion en Tokio, Parte 2: Luchando por Mama
description: Durante una visita al parque de diversiones de Luchadores de Sumo, el equipo Tennyson asiste a una verdadera lucha de sumo como parte de los Juegos Globales. Pero cuando los dañinos gemelos Twain irrumpen en el evento para vengar a su madre, Ben debe pensar las cosas detenidamente si quiere detener a esta polarizada familia.

title: Big Brother/Hiding Place/Rainy Day/Rakes the Leaves/Goes Shopping
description: Caillou remembers when he first met his sister./Caillou is at his Grandparents' house./It's a rainy day and Caillou wants to jump in all the puddles./Caillou and Rosie have so much fun playing in the leaves./Caillou is looking forward to making a snowman.

title: Azulejo
description: Steven cuestiona los motivos de una misteriosa fusión que de repente se presenta en su casa.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Duelo en la Piscina
description: Unikitty y la pandilla se están divirtiendo mucho en la piscina pública, hasta que intentan que Perricornio nade en la parte profunda con ellos. A Perricornio le da muchísimo miedo ir a lo más profundo. Ahora Unikitty y la banda deben ayudarlo a superar su miedo para que se divierta al máximo en la piscina. Mientras tanto, Master Frown y Brock están tramando un plan para arruinar la diversión de todos: quitar el tapón de la piscina. Ahora Perricornio debe dominar su miedo para detener a los que quieren estropear la diversión.

title: La Cosa en la Pared
description: Cuando Axel y el equipo acusan a Galileo de robar sus posesiones, el lagarto debe cazar al verdadero culpable, una misteriosa criatura detrás del muro, para demostrar su inocencia.

title: Los Opuestos se Atraen
description: Afirmando que es bueno de corazón, Dynamo convence a Axel y al equipo para que lo ayuden a encontrar una batería que pueda alimentar su centrífuga y liberarlo del control de Madtrap, pero Bobbie Blobby no está comprando la historia del malo.

title: Finding Posada
description: When Victor and Valentino attempt to win the grand prize of best ofrenda at the Dia de Muertos festival, they enlist the help of legendary artist Jose Guadalupe Posada himself!

title: Cat Fingers
description: Steven attempts to master the power of shape shifting, but can only shape shift his fingers into tiny cat heads.

title: Band For Life
description: When Vic and Val tag along with Xochi to a punk concert, they want to prove that they're cool enough to hang out with her. But in a desperate attempt to be cool, they wind up destroying the concert.

title: Ghost Camp
description: Lucas and his friends are camping in the garden. Avocado tells them all a spooky story around the campfire. This makes Lucas really uneasy and he thinks there's a ghostie in the garden.

title: No Sleep Sleepover
description: It's a sleepover at the castle and Unikitty and Puppycorn want to stay up all night, believing something magical must happen if you stay up long enough.​ At first the friends are game to stay up all night, but as they fall asleep one by one, Unikitty worries they won't make it! How far will she and her bro go to stay awake, and will they discover the secret reason people are supposed to go to bed when the Sandman shows up?

title: A Yoorg Awakening
description: Funshine's jokes unwittingly hurt the feelings of a strange Rock Giant. Disturbed from its slumber, the usually benign creature inadvertently creates havoc for the Whiffles until Funshine calms it by apologizing.

title: The Second Stage Begins/Mechanoids Attack!
description: The Second Stage Begins: With half of the brawlers eliminated, the second stage of the Bakugan Battle league begins. This round will be a timed race to the finish, with all kinds of tricks and traps that will slow down even the best brawlers./Mechanoids Attack!: Mechanoids have crashed the second stage of the Bakugan Battle League, causing all kinds of havoc. The Awesome Brawlers will now have to race against the clock, battling competitors and mechanoids if they want to make it through this round.

title: Hachiman
description: While on a super important mission to get batteries for the TV remote Lion-O meets Hachiman, a cool Samurai warrior. Now Lion-O will do anything to prove he's just as cool as Hachiman, even if it means risking his own life!

title: Jewel of the Aisle/Super Zeroes
description: Jewel of the Isle: A crook hides a huge diamond in a box of the girls' favorite cereal. But how can he trick the girls into giving him some cereal in order to get the jewel back?/Super Zeroes: The girls don't think they have enough superhero accessories like those found in the comic books. They begin to emulate their favorite characters, complete with gadgets and gizmos.

title: #IllusionsOfGrandeur
description: Ready to emerge from her father's shadow, Zee Zatara secretly seeks fame and acclaim performing for her own audience at the pier. But when her act is dismissed as fakery, she loses her cool and accidentally unleashes mischievous gremlins who run wild all over the pier.

title: La Trampa de Madcap
description: Madcap y Princess SugarSalt atrapan a Axel y al equipo dentro de un laberinto impulsado por Minergy que los ataca con sus mayores temores, obligándolos a trabajar juntos y escapar como una unidad.

title: Nancy's Fireman Calendar
description: While distracted by a new scientific endeavor, Seth winds up ruining his mom's treasured fireman calendar! After his attempt to make it up to her puts them both in danger, Seth finally learns the importance of communicating with his mom.

title: Ballroom
description: MG fixes up the ballroom and warns UG and PS not to step a foot in there until he gets a chance to use it.  But UG mistakenly tosses a ball into the room.  Now PS and UG have to retrieve the ball without touching one foot to the ground.

title: Digital Quality
description: Ben and Gwen don't want to go to the CD Library. CDs are for old people. Ew. Once Team Tennyson is there, Lord Decibel traps them inside and demands a ransom. Ben and Gwen find Kevin inside on a potentially nefarious quest of his own, but it turns out that Lord Decibel may have already found the item that they so desperately desire.

title: The Visitor
description: A mysterious alien named Xylene shows up and wants to return the Omnitrix to its rightful owner, Grandpa Max!

title: I Don't Need a Hat
description: Craig decides to ditch his hat on a chilly day and it becomes a battle for body heat.

title: Steven's Lion
description: Steven makes friends with a magical lion, but can't quite tell why it likes him.

title: #WorldsFinest
description: When PR whiz Max Lord tells Batgirl and Supergirl he can improve their image by doing publicity stunts, the two friends forget what being a hero is really about.

title: The Friend
description: Gumball and Darwin help Anais make up an imaginary friend who turns out to be all too real. Anais throws a party but no-one shows up as she has no friends or social skills. Gumball and Darwin help Anais make up an imaginary friend who, much to all their surprise, appears in front of them. Gumball and Darwin teach Anais and her new friend how to become friends, but soon realise that he might not be so imaginary after all...

title: Super Black Friday
description: After being forced to work on a holiday, KO, Rad and Enid take a stand.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: Squideo Games
description: When Vambre and Prohyas are hired for separate gigs, they end up having to battle each other to claim a rare Squideo from Lake Sprite in Galacton.

title: This is My Jam
description: Rigby gets a terrible, terrible song stuck in his head and will go to any lengths to get it out.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: ERabbitcator/Marvin Flag Gag: Planet Split in 2/The Sales Duck
description: Bugs must outsmart a new technological foe. Elmer is ready for bed, but persistent salesman Daffy stands in the way of a good night's rest.

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Salchichas y Dulce Golpe
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben superar sus obsesiones por las salchichas y los videojuegos.

title: Booster's Gold
description: Green Arrow becomes involved with Booster Gold when he discovers that the self-centered superhero has brought dinosaurs back from the past for a money-making venture.

title: Kitty & Hawk
description: When Puppycorn's favorite toy goes missing, Unikitty & Hawkodile team up to track down the thief, buddy-cop style! But when things get tough and the case goes cold, now it's not just their partnership on the line, but their friendship!

title: Sofa Cama
description: Cuando los Piratas del Cielo se infiltran en el cuartel general del sheriff, iponen en peligro a los héroes!

title: Poorbucks
description: When Morbucks loses her money, Blossom tries to reform her.

title: Jam
description: Harley Quinn, Poison Ivy, and Catwoman recruit Starfire and Raven for their roller deby team.

title: Big Jumping Spider
description: When Findley comments to Lucas that his jump isn't very long or high Lucas ramps things up, jumping higher and longer in ever increasing death defying jumps. Findley is now beginning to regret his comment and wishes Lucas wouldn't jump so far. This all culminates in Lucas going for the big one in his car down a track. Can Findley convince him not too?

title: This Spells Disaster
description: The gang is planning a surprise for Puppycorn, so they spell things out when talking so he won't find out. Desperate to know what they're saying, Puppycorn finds a magic book that he thinks will help him learn to spell, but unbeknownst to him, it's teaching him how to cast spells! Will Puppycorn realize that knowledge is power and some secrets are kept for a reason?

title: Blocks
description: Meet Bing and his friends… Join us and celebrate the noisy, joyful, messy reality of preschool life.

title: El Reino del Jamas
description: Los ninja llegan al Never-Realm donde rápidamente se sienten abrumados. Afortunadamente, son recibidos por una tribu de pescadores de hielo que les dicen que Zane ha sido encarcelado por el malvado Emperador de hielo.

title: Cool Guy Clarence
description: When Clarence meets JT, the kid who mows their lawn, he finds a fast friend who shows him some cool new music, a new outlook on life and a sweet rat-tail! Clarence leans into the rat tail lifestyle, discovering a whole new side of Aberdale he never knew existed.

title: To Tame the Perilous Skies!
description: With Axel's drone-wing broken, the team must find another way to stop Madcap and his minions as they take to the skies in toy airplanes for an aerial assault on the city park.

title: Mi Manada
description: A Chloe, una niña prodigio, le resulta difícil conectarse con sus compañeros de clase, que son mucho mayores que ella. Los Osos deciden cuidarla y mostrarle cómo hacerse grandes amigos en la universidad.

title: Cat Burglar
description: While Tiggy and Boss work hard to cover their tracks after they're caught up in a cat burglary, a new churro cart catches Gweeseek's eye.

title: Learns to Drive/Big Friend/Colors/Mails a Letter/Learns to Swim
description: Caillou loves anything to do with cars./Caillou meets a new friend called André./Caillou visits Grandma's house./Mom is upset when the mailman only brings bills./Caillou goes to the swimming pool with his family and Daddy teaches him how to swim.

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: Fortune Cookie
description: Rigby swaps fortune cookie fortunes with Benson.

title: Stuck on You
description: Tired of Axel and the team taking him for granted, Masko tries to get kidnapped and ends up stuck to Dynamo, who's less than enthused with his rubbery new sidekick.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Jake the Dog
description: Jake and Prismo watch from the portal as the Ice King's crown makes Finn more and more powerful.

title: Thanksgiving
description: When Raven's father Trigon shows up for Thanksgiving dinner, Robin's seating plan isn't the only thing that gets ruined.

title: Tokyo Fun Part 1: Big Bugg Bash
description: While in Tokyo, Team Tennyson comes face to face with a horrible secret, Japan's hottest new restaurant is being run by the Bugg Brothers as a nefarious scheme to make loads of money off an unsuspecting public.

title: Sausage and Sweetie Smash
description: Onion must stop Apple from falling prey to his obsession, but a certain phone game is proving to be quite an obstacle.

title: Sleeper Sofa
description: When the Sky Pirates infiltrate Sheriff HQ, they put our heroes in danger!

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Big Trouble in Little Aberdale
description: After stumbling upon a mysterious new kid in their neighborhood , Clarence, Jeff and Sumo decide to take the kid out on the town showing him the fun of junk food, arcades and soda! However, this new lifestyle may be more then the new kid bargained for.

title: The Squashening
description: To escape a monster, the girls have to tell him a scary story.

title: Growing Up is Hard to Do
description: Ben and Gwen are stoked to enter a skating competition, but when Nanny Nightmare shows up to teach the skater kids some manners by turning them into babies, it's up to Team Tennyson to up their game if they are to have any chance at saving the day.

title: Pool Duel
description: Unikitty and the gang are having a great time at the public pool, until they try to get Puppycorn to swim in the deep end with them. Puppycorn is terrified of the deep end. Now Unikitty and the gang must get him over his fear, so he can have maximum pool fun. Meanwhile, Master Frown and Brock are hatching a plan to ruin everyone's fun, by pulling the pool's plug.

title: Serious Steven
description: Steven tries to prove himself to be a worthy Crystal Gem to Garnet while they navigate their way out of an ancient Gem maze.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Cats Do Dance
description: In order to save their alley, Top Cat and his gang are forced into a dance battle.

title: Electric Buttercup
description: Buttercup gets more than she bargained for when she makes a deal with a cool '80s metalhead to get a sweet new guitar.

title: Eggscellent
description: Mordecai wants to win a hat for Rigby.

title: Escape From Bebe Bay
description: When Vic & Val accidentally turn themselves and Don into babies, they must escape a daycare center in order to change back to their normal ages.

title: El baile de los Infusionistas
description: Los Infusionistas organizan un baile e invitan a todos los habitantes del bosque. Craig cree que el único propósito del baile es hacerle una broma a él, mientras que Kelsey debe lidiar con un admirador indeseado.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: The Never-Realm
description: The ninja arrive in the Never-Realm where they quickly find themselves overwhelmed. Luckily, they are taken in by a tribe of Ice Fishers who tell them Zane has been imprisoned by the evil Ice Emperor.

title: In the Clouds
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a boy get his head out of the clouds and focused on his history test.

title: Black Friday
description: Starfire is visited by three ghosts and shown the true meaning of Black Friday.

title: Bluebird
description: Steven questions the motives of a mysterious fusion that suddenly shows up at his house.

title: Volleyball
description: Steven is determined to help Pink Diamond's original Pearl heal the scar on her face.

title: CodE.T.
description: When Cody gets sick, the kids want send a message back to his home planet in hopes that they can save him, but Courtney is not in favor of this plan.

title: An Unlikely Ally
description: Lloyd runs afoul of the Ice Emperor's Blizzard Samurai but is rescued by a strange wolf with whom an unlikely friendship develops.

title: Opposites Attract
description: Claiming he's good at heart, Dynamo convinces Axel and the team to help him find a battery that can power his centrifuge and free him from Madtrap's control - but Bobbie Blobby isn't buying the baddie's story.

title: A Cold Goodbye
description: Having learned Zane is not dead, Master Wu prepares to go after him, but Lloyd and the other ninja take matters into their own hands and defy their Master.

title: Furniture & Meat
description: Big money problems send Finn and Jake to Wildberry Kingdom.

title: Pumm-Ra
description: Mumm-Ra plans to disguise himself as a Thunderian and infiltrate Cats' Lair, but the Ancient Spirits of Evil are mad at him and won't give him any magic today. No matter, Mumm-Ra knows what a ThunderCat looks like so he slaps on some awful, unconvincing, cat make up and heads to Cats' Lair to introduce himself!

title: Carrie
description: Darwin se propone encontrar una foto de Carrie para la portada del anuario escolar, pero ambos terminan recordando todas sus travesuras espeluznantes del pasado.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: It's a Mad, Mad, Mad Ben World Part 1
description: Alternate dimensions, duplicate Bens and villains from throughout time and space! Just another day in Bellwood.

title: Super Dia de Ofertas
description: Cuando los obligan a trabajar en un día festivo, KO, Rad y Enid se pronuncian en contra de la medida.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: The Points
description: Gumball and Darwin discover Tobias is doing way better than them in an online game called Galatrek. Tobias admits he earns good points doing chores for his parents, which he then exchanges for dollars to buy cool stuff for Galatrek. If Gumball and Darwin do Tobias' chores they can earn his good points and use them for Galatrek. Gumball and Darwin think they've hit the jackpot. But these good points may not be quite as good as Tobias claims.

title: Apple's Formula
description: Apple needs to find a formula for comedy that will land him a movie role.

title: Fat Cats
description: Teen Titans Go takes a comedic look at the superheroes' lives. Viewers finally get the opportunity to watch what life is like for the super teens when their capes are left at home. The teens will deal with everyday issues of adolescence including laundry contests and quests to construct the perfect sandwich.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Una Fria Despedida
description: Habiendo aprendido que Zane no está muerto, el Maestro Wu se prepara para ir tras él, pero Lloyd y el otro ninja toman el asunto en sus propias manos y desafían a su Maestro.

title: Los Vegetales
description: Gumball y Darwin solo quieren holgazanear todo el día, pero terminan teniendo que salvar al resto de la familia.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: #SmallVictories
description: A malfunctioning device shrinks Karen into the Microverse, leaving technophobic Diana as her only hope.

title: Comfort Level
description: Sylvester learns to live without his blankey.

title: It's a Mad, Mad, Mad Ben World Part 2
description: Ben and Dr. Psychobos become reluctant allies in a parallel-dimension maelstrom.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Tiger Millionaire
description: Steven joins Amethyst in an underground wrestling league.

title: Manzallin
description: Manzana y Cebollín quieren llevarse el crédito de haber creado una nueva moda de baile.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Rules of the Game
description: When Thomas builds an obstacle course for his friends, he gets upset when they won't play with it HIS way.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Berb-cules
description: The ThunderCats finally sit the Berbils down and tell them they really shouldn't be building things for the Mutants anymore, it's time for the Berbils to stand up for themselves. The Berbils take this advice way too far and build a giant, building-sized, Berbil named Berbcules. Berb-cules takes back everything the Berbils ever built for the Mutants and everything they ever built for the ThunderCats! Now Panthro has to figure out a way to a defeat the most powerful invention the best little builders have ever built!

title: The Five Rules of Finding
description: Tiggy and Gweeseek use Chief's Five Rules of Finding to discover their own method of finding and locating Boss' missing tie.

title: Selfish Shellfish
description: Apple and Onion are faced with a philosophical question: Are they truly doing good deeds for the good of other people or is it all just for them?

title: Pegado a Ti
description: Cansado de que Axel y el equipo lo den por sentado, Masko intenta ser secuestrado y termina atrapado en Dynamo, que está menos que entusiasmado con su nuevo compañero de goma.

title: #NoDerribenElArbol
description: Jessica Cruz y Pam Isley se unen para evitar que un antiguo árbol sea talado, pero ninguna se da cuenta de quien es el alter ego de la otra ni los extremos a los que llegarán para proteger lo que es importante.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: License to Deliver
description: When Percy has to deliver a new light bulb to the lighthouse at night, Thomas suggests playing secret agents along the way to help Percy forget about his fear of the dark.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: All Aboard the Space Train
description: In a strange turn of events, the JLA enlist the help of Space Cabbie and Jonah Hex to stop the hijacking of an intergalactic space train.

title: Thank You for Watching the Show
description: When KO finds moments of his life slipping by, he begins to suspect something weird is going on.

title: Losing Ice
description: Feeling unappreciated, Ice Bear leaves his brothers to be the chef of a restaurant. Desperate to fill the void, Grizz and Panda look for Ice Bear's replacement.

title: Ego - Egoista
description: Manzana y Cebolla tienen que demostrar que no son egoístas cuando hacen sus buenas acciones.

title: The Awkwardness
description: Gumball is walking in the same direction as Hot Dog Guy, and with each step it becomes increasingly awkward.

title: Imaginary Fiend/Cootie Gras
description: Imaginary Fiend: The new boy in school has a special friend nobody else can see. When this imaginary friend begins destroying the class, the girls must imagine how to stop him./Cootie Gras: Mojo observes that everyone is staying away from little Harry Pitt because he has cooties. So Mojo concocts a plan to keep the girls away by using this cootie-covered boy as bait.

title: Bakugan Battle League, Tokyo Edition/Battle Royal
description: Bakugan Battle League, Tokyo Edition: It's the start of the Bakugan Battle League - Toyko edition! The first round will be a Battle Royale style competition, where only half the competitors will make it through to the next round. Along with the Awesome brawlers the field of competitors is filled with familiar friends and foes./Battle Royal: The first round of the Bakugan Battle League - Tokyo edition continues. The Awesome Brawler's and their Bakugan battle their way through the challenge and face off against tough competitors.

title: Fly, Chase, Fly
description: Chep is disappointed Mush-Mush and Lilit are too busy leaf-gliding to play moss-ball with him, so he hangs out with a new weevil friend instead. But Chep's new friend must migrate with all the other weevils. Except he doesn't know how to fly! Chep must teach him to fly while overcoming his own secret fear of heights.

title: Un Aliado Peculiar
description: Lloyd se enfrenta a los Samurais Blizzard del Emperador de Hielo, pero es rescatado por un lobo extraño con quien desarrolla una amistad peculiar.

title: #DetentionClub
description: Five socially disparate teens, Hal, Pam, Kara, Zee and Garth, find they have more in common than they thought after spending a Saturday in detention.

title: The Return
description: Ghostfreak has returned! And he has brought a Mummy, Werewolf and Frankenstein like aliens with him to help him shroud the Earth in darkness.

title: Must Be Jelly!
description: Cindy comes up with a novel way to get more time to get everything done.

title: Bad Heir Day
description: Princess Zange's Autostyle Magisword is stolen and it's up to the Warriors to retrieve it so their royal leader can face her subjects without bad hair.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: La Taza del Patito de la Suerte
description: Cuando Adorabat y Colosal rompen la taza favorita de Mao Mao, el sheriff los castiga con su silencio.

title: Kitty y Halcon: Protectores de la Ley
description: Cuando el juguete favorito de Perricornio desaparece, Unikitty y Halcondrilo se unen para localizar al ladrón, ial estilo socios policías! Pero cuando las cosas se ponen difíciles y el caso no se resuelve, ya no es solo su sociedad la que está en juego, sino también su amistad.

title: Tokyo Fun Part 2: Slamming It Up
description: While on a visit to the Sumo Slammers Amusement Park in Tokyo, Team Tennyson gets to watch a genuine sumo wrestling match as part of the Global Games, but when the mischievous Twain Twins crash the event to avenge their mother's medal snub years earlier, Ben must think things through if he is to stop the polarizing family!

title: The Best Burger in the World
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to finish their chores before they can have burgers.

title: Pijamada sin Dormir
description: Hay una fiesta de pijamas en el castillo, y Unikitty y Perricornio quieren quedarse despiertos toda la noche, porque creen que algo mágico debe suceder si te quedas despierto el tiempo suficiente. Al principio, los amigos están dispuestos a quedarse despiertos toda la noche. Pero cuando comienzan a quedarse dormidos de a uno, ia Unikitty le preocupa que no lo logren! ¿Hasta dónde llegarán ella y su hermano para mantenerse despiertos, y descubrirán la razón secreta por la que se supone que la gente debe irse a la cama cuando aparece El Arenero?

title: Who's on the Phone?
description: Pocoyo finds a phone. He has to work out what it's for, and who's on the other end of the line. It's Elly inviting everyone to a party!

title: Thank You
description: The Snow Golem and his beseeching pup pay a visit to the Fire Kingdom.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Nobody's Perfect
description: When Cheer makes some simple mistakes, she begins to lose confidence in her piloting skills and herself. The self-doubt becomes so severe, she decides to step away from her role as pilot of the Cloudseeker. But the Team needs her, the Whiffles need her, and she must regain her self-confidence so they can stop Bluster's latest nefarious scheme.
